## Cycle C1 — Token rewire + focus ring

**Goal:** `public/css/variables.css` becomes single source of theme truth. `[data-theme="dark"] :root` reassigns semantic tokens. `--ring` token + global `:focus-visible` rule. Reduced-motion guard in `base.css`.

**Success signal:** Toggling theme flips every surface via token flow only. Tab-key navigation shows visible focus halo on every interactive element in light + dark. No visual regressions vs baseline.

### C1 Files

- **Modify** `public/css/variables.css` (expand from ~184L to ~360L)
- **Modify** `public/css/base.css` (add `:focus-visible` + `prefers-reduced-motion`)

