## Cycle C2 — State pills + analytics wiring + drilled/locked contrast

**Goal:** Four analytics tile-state pills read at a glance (green solid / lavender primed / amber drilled / mauve locked + danger misconceptions). `.analytics-select` consumes `--surface-card`.

### C2 Files

- **Modify** `public/css/components.css` (add `.pill--*` variants)
- **Modify** `public/css/ai-runs-dashboard.css` (wire analytics-select to token; apply pill variants)

