- [ ] **Step 0: Add `--node-*-rgb` channel tokens to `variables.css`**

In C1 the scalar `--node-*` tokens were added. For `rgba()` compositing pill backgrounds + borders, add matching `-rgb` channels. Append inside `:root` alongside the node-state tokens from C1:

```css
