  --node-locked-rgb:     202, 196, 206;   /* mauve-200 */
  --node-primed-rgb:     141, 134, 201;   /* lavender-500 */
  --node-drilled-rgb:    216, 168, 103;   /* warm amber */
  --node-solidified-rgb:  77, 186, 138;   /* success green */
```

- [ ] **Step 1: Add pill variants to `components.css` (token-only, no hex literals)**

Append at end of file:

```css
/* ============================================================
   State pills — four learner node states + danger.
   Consumed by analytics, graph legend, concept status rows.
   Colors sourced from --node-* tokens; never hex literals.
   ============================================================ */
.pill {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 6px;
  padding: 4px 12px;
  border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  border: 1px solid transparent;
  background: var(--pill-accent-bg);
  color: var(--accent-primary);
}
.pill--solid {
  background: rgba(var(--node-solidified-rgb), 0.14);
  color: var(--pill-success-text);
  border-color: rgba(var(--node-solidified-rgb), 0.24);
}
.pill--primed {
  background: rgba(var(--node-primed-rgb), 0.18);
  color: rgba(var(--ink-900-rgb), 0.82);
  border-color: rgba(var(--node-primed-rgb), 0.30);
}
.pill--drilled {
  background: rgba(var(--node-drilled-rgb), 0.18);
  color: rgba(var(--node-drilled-rgb), 1);
  border-color: rgba(var(--node-drilled-rgb), 0.32);
}
.pill--locked {
  background: rgba(var(--node-locked-rgb), 0.32);
  color: rgba(var(--ink-900-rgb), 0.58);
  border-color: rgba(var(--node-locked-rgb), 0.50);
}
.pill--danger {
  background: var(--pill-danger-bg);
  color: var(--pill-danger-text);
  border-color: rgba(224, 92, 107, 0.24);
}
[data-theme="dark"] .pill--primed {
  color: var(--cream-50);
}
[data-theme="dark"] .pill--drilled {
  color: rgba(var(--node-drilled-rgb), 1);
  filter: brightness(1.2);
}
[data-theme="dark"] .pill--locked {
  color: rgba(var(--cream-50-rgb), 0.62);
}
```

