- **Modify** `public/css/layout.css` (hide drawer-toggle + map-close-btn in map view; add `.map-back-link` rule)
- **Modify** `public/js/app.js` (add `.map-back-link` click wiring in map-view render path; add `title` tooltip on drawer-toggle for UX-todo #26)

